{"tid":740432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒，珀麗灣班業主貪得無厭，輸打贏要，長期以黎都係成班刁民","createTime":"2018-07-13T01:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T09:52:23.000Z","uid":46849,"like":41,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8b2937452d00b400c6dfba0fb76755f8ba8d30","tid":740432,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"明明多人搭巴士<br />\n極少人搭船<br />\n咁咪多d 巴士少d 船<br />\n又唔係 cut 晒<br />\n但係唔俾<br />\n<br />\n明明自己個單位升咁多<br />\n再加埋通脹<br />\n都唔比人地加價<br />\n次次都嘈<br />\n人地做唔住又話關佢鬼事<br />\n要用公帑貼<br />\n<br />\n一句咩最初承諾乜乜物物<br />\n傾都唔肯傾<br />\n一人讓一步妥協下都唔肯<br />\n比我係新紅雞都唔撚制啦<br />\n你玩合約<br />\n咪玩合約囉<br />\n之後又嘈<br />\n<br />\n成班中產業主自私到仆街<br />\n死撚晒佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e4fa5b0075f68ff06020261c392a95e55291b1","tid":740432,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd28603c624d570be4f5c650e64a136efedf73e","tid":740432,"uid":46849,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"然後最叻就屈人打手五毛<br />\n<br />\n成班生番都唔撚講道理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4ef5bf04bb7774ecd624b8be7ea5bf00744029","tid":740432,"uid":23993,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"啱呀呢種思維<br />\n所以港鐵咪年年賺錢但又年年照加你價囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a391c11510e54ab94c62b8d5f5ec07a0f02b528f","tid":740432,"uid":46849,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1b4ef5bf04bb7774ecd624b8be7ea5bf00744029","tid":740432,"uid":23993,"like":5,"dislike":9